                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Visellius <lb n="2"/>Germanus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Ap</abbr><ex>ollinaris</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr><am><g type="centuria"/></am></abbr><ex>centuria</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Petro<lb break="no" n="5"/>ni <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>sti</abbr><ex>pendiorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>XII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende, zusammengesetzte Fragmente. Bruchlinie quer durch den unteren Teil des Inschriftfeldes ab der letzten Zeile. Zeile 1 (Ende): S außerhalb des Inschriftfeldes stehend; LI-Ligatur; Zeile 2 (Ende): S klein; Zeile 3: MIL-Ligatur; Zeile 5: NI-, XXX-Ligatur. Betz: Teilpublikation der Inschrift.</p>
            </div>
